INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (75, 2, '2011-12-15 23:03:27', '2011-12-15 17:33:27', 'TapToTrack is the data entry for the TrendTrack package.\n\nTapToTrack is a mobile application that can be used on any Android device for data input through touch based interaction.\n\nFeatures of TapToTrack :\n\n1. Gender and Age based classifications :\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">The application has a single screen with areas distinctly marked by different colors for Gender and Age based categorization.</p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_73" align="alignnone" width="235" caption="TapToTrack"]<a href="http://radsinnovativesolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Categories.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-73" title="TapToTrack - Gender and Age Classification" src="http://radsinnovativesolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Categories-235x300.png" alt="TapToTrack - Gender and Age Classification" width="235" height="300" /></a>[/caption]\n\n2. One Click Download and Install :\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">TapToTrack, being an Android app, can be installed effortlessly by simply clicking on a link.</p>\n3. Device rotation :\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">The same device can be used in many stores (moved from one store to another), due to the database selection option. Choice of selection of database on the software allows input of data into the appropriate database.</p>\n4. Fast response time :\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">The application is fit for fast taps. Conventional mechanical click counters take about a second for their springs to return to original state. This can lead to loss of data during peak hours. TapToTrack on the other hand, is sensitive to Taps one every 100 milliseconds.</p>\n5. Group data :\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Multiple taps for the same kind of data is avoided with TapToTrack. TapToTrack has group count in order to indicate number of members belonging to the same category. Tapping once with a higher count avoids the need to tap repeatedly.</p>\n6. Automatic Live Data Sync :\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">The data captured by TapToTrack is sent to the database on frequent intervals, thereby providing a near live data viewing experience for the TrendView users. Also, data is not lost on quitting of application, and is sent in the background.</p>\n7. Reversal of Data not possible :\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Data once in, cannot be modified by members in chain-of-command.</p>\n8. MOBILE / WIFI Internet :\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">TapToTrack is compatible with both Mobile packet data internet connection, and a Wireless (Wi-Fi) data connection. This ensures that TapToTrack can be used in any type of location (Area crowded? Packed with walls for signal? -&gt; use Wi-FI. Too costly to set-up wireless infrastructure? -&gt; use Mobile packet data)</p>\nReasons for Android ?\n\n- Android devices available at very reasonable rates. (~3000 INR)\n\n- Most widely used mobile OS.\n\n- Inter-Compatible and Backward-Compatible.\n\n- Seamless updating and upgrading.', 'TapToTrack', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '32-revision-2', '', '', '2011-12-15 23:03:27', '2011-12-15 17:33:27', '', 32, 'http://radsinnovativesolutions.com/?p=75', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
